Merch Calendar

Plan ahead with key dates for every month. This calendar highlights when to start, order, and deliver merch around major events so you can stay ahead all year long.

INSTANT RECOGNITION

Get What You Want, When You Want!

Planning ahead is the key to a successful branded merchandise campaign, and our Merchandise Calendar is here to help. This interactive, color-coded guide outlines the ideal timeline for each stage of your project—from brainstorming product ideas to placing your order, tracking production, and ensuring on-time delivery for your event. Use this as a reference to stay ahead and make informed decisions, but please note: all dates are estimates and subject to change based on product availability, production schedules, and shipping timelines. This calendar serves as a general guide to help you strategize, ensuring your branded merchandise arrives exactly when you need it.
